text: Bee Hoon Goreng Puteh is powerful! Prata is not bad too. Spacious neighbourhood coffeeshop.

Damn shiok!! Pratas here have been consistently good for over a decade. Get them hot at 10am and your day is settled already. Service is always swell and their dhal is on point (mutton base with lots of cloves). Yum.
Service is too slow. If you want to eat here expect to wait 45 min.
Always canceling grab food order. Rubbish.
One of the best mamak places in Bukit gombak.
